"Change Set:		9604Protocols-ar.25Protocols-ar.25:Avoid dictionary protocol in Smalltalk."!!StringHolder methodsFor: '*Protocols-Tools' stamp: 'ar 3/5/2010 21:01'!browseFullProtocol	"Open up a protocol-category browser on the value of the receiver's current selection.    If in mvc, an old-style protocol browser is opened instead.  Someone who still uses mvc might wish to make the protocol-category-browser work there too, thanks."	| aClass |	(Smalltalk isMorphic and: [Smalltalk hasClassNamed: #Lexicon]) ifFalse: [^ self spawnFullProtocol].	((aClass := self selectedClassOrMetaClass) notNil and: [aClass isTrait not]) ifTrue:		[(Smalltalk at: #Lexicon) new openOnClass: aClass showingSelector: self selectedMessageName]! !